1. *Kuća* je moja sreća. (The house is my happiness.)
2. Ona ima potpuno novu *kuću*. (She has a brand new house.)
3. *Kućama* su se svi divili. (Everyone admired the houses.)
4. U *kući* smo poslednjih nekoliko meseci. (We have been in the house for the past few months.)
5. Oni su gradili *kuću* od zida do zida. (They built the house from wall to wall.)
6. Poštuj svoju *kuću*. (Respect your house.)